# Community structure for the repository.
# To use: copy this file to communities.txt in the same directory, adjust
# it for your institution, and redeploy (or run setup-communities.sh).
#
# Format:
#   Community Name|Description          top-level community
#   > Sub-community Name|Description    sub-community of the last community
#   >> Collection Name|Description      collection in the last sub-community

Faculty of Engineering|Research, projects and theses from the Faculty of Engineering
> Department of Civil Engineering|Civil Engineering research and student projects
> Department of Electrical Engineering|Electrical Engineering research and student projects
> Department of Mechanical Engineering|Mechanical Engineering research and student projects
> Department of Electronics|Electronics research and student projects

Faculty of Business Studies|Research, reports and theses from the Faculty of Business Studies
> Department of Accounting|Accounting research and student projects
> Department of Business Management|Business Management research and student projects
> Department of Marketing|Marketing research and student projects
> Department of Human Resources Management|Human Resources Management research and student projects

Faculty of Applied Sciences|Research, reports and theses from the Faculty of Applied Sciences
> Department of Food Technology|Food Technology research and student projects
> Department of Chemistry|Chemistry research and student projects
> Department of Biology|Biology research and student projects

Faculty of Information Technology|Research, projects and theses from the Faculty of Information Technology
> Department of Computer Science|Computer Science research and student projects
> Department of Information Systems|Information Systems research and student projects
> Department of Networking and Telecommunications|Networking and Telecommunications research and student projects

Faculty of Art and Design|Creative works, research and theses from the Faculty of Art and Design
> Department of Fine Art|Fine Art works and student projects
> Department of Fashion Design|Fashion Design works and student projects
